          <h4 id="cdbrootaccess">Enable root user for Cloud Database</h4>
          This script will enable the root user for a Cloud Database Instance. Depending on what modifications you make to your Database after enableing thismay keep Rackspace from being able to fully support your Database. 
          <pre class="script-container" data-scriptname="cdbrootaccess"></pre>
        
          <h4 id="makecdbbackup">Create a Cloud Database Backup</h4>
          This script will create a Database backup of the database that you choose.
          <pre class="script-container" data-scriptname="backupdatabase"></pre>

          <h4 id="scheduledbackup">Create Scheduled Database Backups</h4>
          This script will create a scheduled backup for your Cloud Database Instance.
          <pre class="script-container" data-scriptname="scheduledbackup-db"></pre>

          <h4 id="listcdbbackups">List Cloud Database backups</h4>
          This script will list all the Database backups that you have in the region you choose. 
          <pre class="script-container" data-scriptname="listdatabasebackups"></pre>
